<spair id='99'>
<s id='en99'>The state-owned mining firm , which had its long-term credit rating cut by Standard&Poor 's in December 2010 , was seeking a $ 150 million facility last year with an all - in rate , which included margin and fees , of 318 basis points , the source told the newspaper .</s>
